window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>THE DEVASTATING CONCLUSION.</b></p> <p>The destructive power of the Artifact on Enceladus is now clear, but ultimately it is Earth that is most at risk. Can anything stop what has begun?</p> <p><b>It might already be too late ...</b></p> <p><b><i>Lineage</i></b><i>, the third book in the </i><b><i>Saturn's Legacy</i></b><i> series, is a sci-fi thriller full of mystery, intrigue, and epic action from the depths of the ocean to the edge of outer space.</i></p>"; 
